Class ExamRoom

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cpsolver.ifs.model.Constraint<V,T>

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<Constraint<Exam,ExamPlacement>>, CanHoldContext, HasAssignmentContext<Exam,ExamPlacement,ExamRoom.ExamRoomContext>

    public class ExamRoom
extends ConstraintWithContext<Exam,ExamPlacement,ExamRoom.ExamRoomContext>
    A room. Only one exam can use a room at a time (period).
